videos.description: Luka Doncic shows off his skills with two difficult shots against the Nuggets.
videos.headline: Luka gets off to hot start with fadeaway jumper and stepback 3

videos.description: Nikola Jokic blocks Luka Doncic which leads to a fast-break finish and foul for Michael Porter Jr.
videos.headline: Jokic stuffs Doncic leading to an and-1 for Porter Jr.

videos.description: The Nuggets go up by 13 on the Mavs after Austin Rivers' first 3-pointer of the season.
videos.headline: Nuggets use great ball movement to find Rivers for corner 3

videos.description: Maxi Kleber comes up with a huge block on Aaron Gordon, and Luka Doncic makes the Nuggets pay with an and-1 on the other end.
videos.headline: Kleber's block on Gordon leads to and-1 for Doncic

videos.description: Luka Doncic gets a little help from the rim on his shot over Aaron Gordon.
videos.headline: Luka gets the roll on tough and-1 over Gordon

videos.description: Boban Marjanovic embraces Serbia teammate Nikola Jokic before the Mavs' clash against the Nuggets.
videos.headline: Boban gives Jokic big bear hug before Mavs-Nuggets

videos.description: Michael Porter Jr. drains a 3-pointer to add an exclamation point to the Nuggets 33-12 run vs. the Mavs.
videos.headline: Porter Jr. splashes deep 3 to cap off Nuggets' big run

videos.description: Bol Bol does it on both ends of the court for the Nuggets.
videos.headline: Bol Bol gets the steal and then throws down massive alley-oop

videos.description: The Nuggets blow out the Mavericks by 31 points on the second game of their back-to-back.
